    "en": {
      "title": "300 tricycles to be electrified",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to Motor Transport Commissioner General Nishantha Weerasinghe, a pilot project to electrify 300 three-wheelers has been started with the support of the United Nations Development Program as a solution to the petroleum crisis that Sri Lanka is facing.",
        "The Commissioner General of Motor Transport added that a special conference to receive proposals for preparing the legal background related to this project will be held on the 30th of the month at the Bandaranaike International Conference Hall in Colombo and the technical and regulations of this project will be discussed there."
      ],
